######### Polygon API HTTP Requests (Localhost Version)

## All Tickers
GET http://localhost:8000/api/reference/tickers?market=stocks&active=true&order=asc&limit=100&sort=ticker

### Ticker Overview
GET http://localhost:8000/api/reference/tickers/AAPL

### Ticker Types
GET http://localhost:8000/api/reference/tickers/types

### Related Tickers
GET http://localhost:8000/api/meta/symbols/AAPL/company

### Aggregate Bars (OHLC)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/aggs/ticker/AAPL/range/1/day/2023-01-01/2023-01-10?adjusted=true&sort=asc&limit=120

### Daily Market Summary
GET http://localhost:8000/api/open-close/stocks/2023-01-09

### Daily Ticker Summary
GET http://localhost:8000/api/open-close/AAPL/2023-01-09?adjusted=true

### Previous Day Bar
GET http://localhost:8000/api/aggs/ticker/AAPL/prev?adjusted=true

### Single Ticker Snapshot
GET http://localhost:8000/api/snapshot/locale/us/markets/stocks/tickers/AAPL

### Full Market Snapshot
GET http://localhost:8000/api/snapshot/locale/us/markets/stocks/tickers?tickers=AAPL,MSFT,AMZN

### Unified Snapshot
GET http://localhost:8000/api/snapshot?ticker.any_of=AAPL,O:AAPL230616C00190000,C:BTCUSD,FX:EURUSD

### Top Market Movers
GET http://localhost:8000/api/snapshot/locale/us/markets/stocks/gainers?include_otc=false

### Trades
GET http://localhost:8000/api/trades/AAPL?timestamp.gte=2023-01-09T09:30:00Z&timestamp.lte=2023-01-09T16:00:00Z&limit=10

### Last Trade
GET http://localhost:8000/api/last/trade/AAPL

### Quotes
GET http://localhost:8000/api/quotes/AAPL?timestamp.gte=2023-01-09T09:30:00Z&timestamp.lte=2023-01-09T16:00:00Z&limit=10

### Last Quote
GET http://localhost:8000/api/last/nbbo/AAPL

### All Option Contracts
GET http://localhost:8000/api/reference/options/contracts?underlying_ticker=AAPL&contract_type=call&expiration_date.gte=2023-06-01&order=asc&limit=10&sort=ticker

### Option Contract Overview
GET http://localhost:8000/api/reference/options/contracts/O:AAPL230616C00190000

### All Indices
GET http://localhost:8000/api/reference/indices?market=indices&order=asc&limit=10&sort=ticker

### Index Overview
GET http://localhost:8000/api/reference/indices/I:SPX

### All Forex Tickers
GET http://localhost:8000/api/reference/tickers?market=fx&active=true&order=asc&limit=10&sort=ticker

### Currency Conversion
GET http://localhost:8000/api/conversion/USD/EUR?amount=100&precision=2

### All Crypto Tickers
GET http://localhost:8000/api/reference/tickers?market=crypto&active=true&order=asc&limit=10&sort=ticker

### Treasury Yields
GET http://localhost:8000/api/indicators/treasury-yields?ticker=US10Y&from=2023-01-01&to=2023-01-31&order=asc&limit=10

### Analyst Ratings
GET http://localhost:8000/api/meta/symbols/AAPL/analysts
